uk.ac.liv.auction
Class RepastSupplyChainSimulation

java.lang.Object
  uchicago.src.sim.engine.SimModelImpl
      uk.ac.liv.auction.RepastSupplyChainSimulation
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, uchicago.src.reflector.DescriptorContainer, uchicago.src.sim.engine.SimEventProducer, uchicago.src.sim.engine.SimModel
public class RepastSupplyChainSimulation
extends uchicago.src.sim.engine.SimModelImpl
implements java.io.Serializable

A RePast model of a supply chain simulation. This application takes as an argument the name of a parameter file describing an auction experiment, and proceeds to run that experiment interactively using the RePast framework. For unattended batch experiments, use the MarketSimulation application.
